Alarming! - AlarmClock enhanced

The standard AlarmClock now with: 
         
  * Named alarms
  * Set volume (0-100%)
  * Increase volume (0-60s)
  * Pause between alerts (0-1000ms)
  * Disable snooze, or set (1-60m)
  * Disable auto-off, or set (1-60m)
  * 24hr/12hr format
  * Silent alarms

Based off of the open-source android AlarmClock
Source code available at http://github.com/lithium/alarming
